\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ttv1665703202809.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ttv1665703202809.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ttv1665703202809.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ttv1665703202809\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Parses an XML document in the specified file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__topic_d136316e1_d136317e1_d136318e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ttv1665703202809_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__codeblock_wzv_dqg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">PARSEFILE(FileName,Validation)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__section_d3m_2qg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d696490e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">PARSEFILE parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__3\"> Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__4\">Name of the file containing the XML document to\n                        be parsed; maximum size is 512 bytes. <p class=\"p\">The file name is resolved according\n                           to the assignment file [FILES] settings, so the file can be local or\n                           remote.</p><p class=\"p\">The encoding of the XML document can be UTF-8 or another\n                           form of encoding (in contrast with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span>).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Validation</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__2\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16274e1_d16275e1_d16276e1__entry__4\">Determines whether the XML parser will validate\n                        the XML it reads.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__section_gnb_mqg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d696490e141\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__p_d136328e1_d136329e1_d136330e1\">If a fatal error occurs during parsing,\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">-151</code> is returned, unless the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation\n            returns a different negative value. In this case that value is returned instead.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">Number</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">Error</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">–57</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">No handler instance set.<p class=\"p\">If you invoke the\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> operation\n                           without having set a handler instance, they will return this error and\n                           will not parse anything.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">–151</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">&lt;UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ttv1665703202809__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">A fatal error has occured but there is no\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation implemented.<p class=\"p\">A\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation is available but it returns\n                           nothing or a value &gt;= 0.</p><p class=\"p\">A fatal error is deemed unrecoverable,\n                           by the SAX parser.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__section_ryv_rqg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d696490e243\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__p_d136334e1_d136335e1_d136336e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> operation invokes\n            the SAX parser built into Uniface and the SAX operations of the handler instance. If any\n            handler operation returns a negative value, parsing stops and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span>\n            returns with that negative value.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ttv1665703202809_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ttv1665703202809__codeblock_nl2_5qg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">activate $50.setHandler($instancename)\nactivate $50.parsefile(\"myxml.xml\", \"T\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532515\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532515\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PARSEFILE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Parses an XML document in the specified file. Explain this code PARSEFILE(FileName,Validation) Copy Parameters Table 1. PARSEFILE parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description FileName String IN Name of the file containing the XML document to be parsed; maximum size is 512 bytes. The file name is resolved according to the assignment file [FILES] settings, so the file can be local or remote. The encoding of the XML document can be UTF-8 or another form of encoding (in contrast with PARSE ). Validation Boolean IN Determines whether the XML parser will validate the XML it reads. Return Values If a fatal error occurs during parsing, -151 is returned, unless the FATALERROR operation returns a different negative value. In this case that value is returned instead. Table 2. Number Error Description 0 Success –57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> No handler instance set. If you invoke the PARSE or PARSEFILE operation without having set a handler instance, they will return this error and will not parse anything. –151 <UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN> A fatal error has occured but there is no FATALERROR operation implemented. A FATALERROR operation is available but it returns nothing or a value >= 0. A fatal error is deemed unrecoverable, by the SAX parser. Description The PARSEFILE operation invokes the SAX parser built into Uniface and the SAX operations of the handler instance. If any handler operation returns a negative value, parsing stops and PARSE returns with that negative value. Explain this code activate $50.setHandler($instancename) activate $50.parsefile(\"myxml.xml\", \"T\") Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}